{"tid":1374502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實葉虎嘅英文名絕對有可能真係Yip Foo?","createTime":"2019-07-27T19:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:49:29.000Z","uid":73381,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9a63c34ddafafb060d4fd12ccb177fcd6332d8","tid":1374502,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"有好多大陸仔黎到香港之後都一樣會用返廣東話拼音嘅英文名<br />\n<br />\n而中聯辦入面仲有條撚樣叫陳冬 我上網搵一搵陳冬個名 發現中國光大都有條友叫陳冬 而英文名係Chan Tung<br />\n<a href=\"https://webb-site.com/dbpub/SFClicensees.asp?p=5437&amp;a=0&amp;h=Y&amp;sort=posdn&amp;d=2005-12-31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com%2Fdbpub%2FSFClicensees.asp%3Fp%3D5437%26a%3D0%26h%3DY%26sort%3Dposdn%26d%3D2005-12-31&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F14429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7a2cc4fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com/dbpub/SFClicensees.asp?p=5437&amp;a=0&amp;h=Y&amp;sort=posdn&amp;d=2005-12-31</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mtTCZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mtTCZP.png&h=9eb7f729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而search 陳冬 光大 會有以下結果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsgJ0do.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsgJ0do.png&h=4ccbee3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲可以證明依兩個陳冬係同一個人？如果可以證明到的話 咁極大機會Yip Foo就係葉虎"},{"pid":"e50da3340bd285b42df41d898a65a0e7ff35343f","tid":1374502,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f1186e28059c83f1d9807f5395b920c16630f6","tid":1374502,"uid":260371,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:16:43.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟都可以有三本特區護照 有一本 同其他個名唔同啦特權階級有乜唔做得"},{"pid":"32f18432c84c06f4f7933ec35b9a0581c47e4ff2","tid":1374502,"uid":51134,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:18:45.000Z","msg":"稍為接觸過社會既大陸人<br />\n<br />\n都會改名洗底